Package org.opends.guitools.uninstaller

Class UninstallLauncher

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.quicksetup.Launcher
      • org.opends.guitools.uninstaller.UninstallLauncher
  • public class UninstallLauncher
extends Launcher
    This class is called by the uninstall command lines to launch the uninstall of the Directory Server. It just checks the command line arguments and the environment and determines whether the graphical or the command line based uninstall much be launched.
